  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371540/extras/947f395a07046d7cfd3d7dab1280cadb.avif?t=1741851952\" width=582 height=251 /></span><br><strong>Main features</strong><br>ARPG where you explore the area, defeat the boss, and aim for the next area.<br><br>Find warpable checkpoints to make your adventure easier.<br><br>You'll be able to see through the enemy's actions, level up, get better equipment, and defeat the enemies that stand in your way!<br><br>If you feel that the battle is not going well, take a look at the situation.<br>Guard, which completely prevents damage, activates when you're not doing anything.<br>It also activates while walking or dashing.<br><br><strong>[Those who might enjoy this game]</strong><br>Those who like hunting action and fighting game boss battles.<br>Those who like to avoid or deal with attacks without using invincible moves.<br>Those who like to observe and make predictions.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1371540/extras/947f395a07046d7cfd3d7dab1280cadb.avif?t=1741851952\" width=582 height=251 /></span><br><strong>Main features</strong><br>ARPG where you explore the area, defeat the boss, and aim for the next area.<br><br>Find warpable checkpoints to make your adventure easier.<br><br>You'll be able to see through the enemy's actions, level up, get better equipment, and defeat the enemies that stand in your way!<br><br>If you feel that the battle is not going well, take a look at the situation.<br>Guard, which completely prevents damage, activates when you're not doing anything.<br>It also activates while walking or dashing.<br><br><strong>[Those who might enjoy this game]</strong><br>Those who like hunting action and fighting game boss battles.<br>Those who like to avoid or deal with attacks without using invincible moves.<br>Those who like to observe and make predictions.",
